# Stock Explorer - your keys
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your own keys. .env is gitignored, so it
# never reaches GitHub. Both keys are read on the SERVER by the Netlify
# functions - they never appear in browser code (the Project 01 lesson).

# Alpha Vantage - free stock data (the price chart).
# Get a free key in ~20 seconds at https://www.alphavantage.co/support/#api-key
# (no card). The free tier allows about 25 lookups per day, which is plenty for
# exploring a few stocks.
ALPHA_VANTAGE_KEY=

# Anthropic - for the AI analysis ("what do these numbers mean?").
# This is the same key from Projects 01 and 10. Get one at
# https://console.anthropic.com (API keys); add a little credit under Billing.
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
